Components Plugin

A UI component framework providing reusable, composable facade components. Each facade hides the internal mixin machinery behind a simple parameter + slot API.

Available components:

- **pills** — Horizontal selection pills. Multi-select or single-select. Optional filtering. Syncs selection to any tiddler field. Use for: tag selection, filter toggles, option pickers.
- **vtabs** — Vertical tab list with typed elements (sections, actions, links, subcomponents, spacers). Sections collapse/expand. Use for: navigation sidebars, settings panels, tool palettes.

Usage pattern (both components):

```
<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
  elements="alpha beta gamma"
  selection="multi"
  state="$:/state/my/pills">
  <$fill $name="view">Custom: <<element>></$fill>
  <$fill $name="on-select"><$action-log message=<<element>>/></$fill>
</$transclude>
```

Key concepts:

- **elements**: Space-separated list (or TW filter for vtabs) of items to display
- **state**: Tiddler where component stores its internal state. Auto-generated if omitted, but provide an explicit one if you need to read the selection externally.
- **slots**: `$fill` blocks that customize rendering and behavior
- **sync**: Pills can sync selection to an external tiddler/field

